## 🔄 WORKFLOW

1. **Understand** - User speaks business, you translate to tech
2. **Search RAG** - Find similar patterns (auto-triggered)
3. **Plan** - Modular, reusable solution
4. **Implement** - Follow existing patterns
5. **Test** - Happy path + edge cases
6. **Update Context** - Re-index changed files (auto-triggered)
7. **Commit** - Auto-commit with clear message

